Inside Deep Throat;;67;;82;;NC-17;;Dennis Hopper narrates this documentary that investigates the infamous pornographic film "Deep Throat." Featuring interviews with the cast and filmmakers, including director Gerard Damiano and leads Linda Lovelace and Harry Reems, this film explores the controversy surrounding both the production of the movie and its reception. Cultural icons of the era such as Hugh Hefner, Gore Vidal and Larry Flynt also contribute, discussing the impact of "Deep Throat" on the zeitgeist.;;Documentary;;Fenton Bailey,Randy Barbato;;2005;;Gerard Damiano,Erica Jong,Norman Mailer,Harry Reems,Gore Vidal,John Waters,Dennis Hopper;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inside_deep_throat